Itu benar.

00:21:41.670 --> 00:21:45.610
Berpose. Tiga, empat! Mulai.

00:21:46.560 --> 00:21:49.090
Lakukanlah. Tunjukkan kepercayaan dirimu.

00:21:49.090 --> 00:21:52.120
Berpose. Oke.

